1. create pods : // use kubectl utility 
kubectl run nginx --image=nginx    //use docker image // if you want to add specific tags to image.

pod/nginx created 

2. if you want to see long details :
kubectl describe pod nginx   // pod name 

3. if you want to see ip,node details:
kubectl get pods -o wide

4. create pod command:
kubectl run

5. create deployment :
kubectl create deployment nginx --image=nginx

